<div id="pf35ce" class="pf w43 h236" data-page-no="35ce"><div class="pc pc35ce w43 h236"><div class="t maf4 x3f h4d ya0b ff3 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Blessing of Daily Study </div><div class="t m10fc x5b h27 y7c8 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Every day some portion of time should be appropriated </div><div class="t m637 x29 h27 yff0 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to the study of the lessons, not merely in learning to me-</div><div class="t mbc x29 h27 ycc0 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">chanically repeat the words, while the mind does not com-</div><div class="t mb5 x29 h27 y594 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prehend the meaning; but to go to the very foundation, and </div><div class="t m36e x29 h27 y15a7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">become familiar with what is brought out in the lesson.&quot; </div><div class="t m5b9 x28 h16 ya10 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">â€”Counsels on Sabbath School Work, </div><div class="t m581 x46 h27 ya10 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 53. </div><div class="t m2051 x1d h4d yd77 ff3 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">My Pledge </div><div class="t m93f x65 h27 y1329 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As one who greatly desires to improve his knowledge of </div><div class="t mcfb x36 h27 y120e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Scriptures, I pledge myself to the careful and prayerful </div><div class="t m60c x29 h27 ya98 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study of some portion of my Sabbath School lesson each </div><div class="t m64d x36 h27 yc09 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">day of the week. </div><div class="t m144c x79 h34 y9c6 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(signed) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
